This minor mode enforce key-bind of Emacs.

[[drill-instructor.el]]

Features:
* He prohibits you from using cursor key. Use C-f,C-b,C-p,C-n!
* He prohibits you from using backspace key. Use C-h!
* He prohibits you from using enter key. Use C-m!
* He prohibits you from using TAB key. Use C-i!

See page in [http://github.com/k1LoW GitHub] https://github.com/k1LoW/emacs-drill-instructor/wiki
